window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Colonel Joe Bishop made a promise and he's going to keep it; taking the captured alien starship Flying Dutchman back out.</p> <p>He doesn't agree when the UN decides to send almost 70 elite Special Operations troops, hotshot pilots, and scientists with him; the mission is a fool's errand he doesn't expect to ever return from. At least, this time, the Earth is safe, right?</p> <p>Not so much.</p>"; 
